          "_name": "features030",
          "_sourceTheme": "startm5",
          "_customHTML": "<section data-bs-version=\"5.1\" class=\"features030\" group=\"Article\" data-bg-video=\"{{bg.type == 'video' && bg.value.url}}\" mbr-class=\"{'mbr-fullscreen': fullScreen,'mbr-parallax-background': bg.parallax}\">\n    <mbr-parameters>\n        <header>Size</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Full Width\" name=\"fullWidth\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Top\" name=\"paddingTop\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"6\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Bottom\" name=\"paddingBottom\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"6\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Reverse\" name=\"reverseContent\">\n        <header>Show/Hide</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Title\" name=\"showTitle\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Text\" name=\"showText\">\n        <input type=\"range\" name=\"imageWidth\" title=\"Image\" min=\"4\" max=\"8\" step=\"1\" value=\"6\">\n        <header>Card</header>\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Card BG\" name=\"cardbg\" value=\"#ffffff\" selected>\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Card Color\" name=\"cardbg\" value=\"#ffffff\" selected>\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Icon Color\" name=\"iconColor\" value=\"#f92c50\" selected>\n        <header>Background</header>\n        <fieldset type=\"background\" name=\"bg\" parallax>\n            <input type=\"image\" title=\"Image\" value=\"@PROJECT_PATH@/assets/images/robomaster2.jpg\" selected>\n            <input type=\"color\" title=\"Color\" value=\"#edefeb\">\n            <input type=\"video\" title=\"Video\" value=\"https://vimeo.com/428046504\">\n        </fieldset>\n        <header condition=\"bg.type === 'video'\">Fallback Image</header>\n        <input type=\"image\" title=\"Fallback Image\" value=\"../_images/background1.jpg\" name=\"fallBackImage\" condition=\"bg.type === 'video'\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Overlay\" name=\"overlay\" condition=\"bg.type !== 'color'\" checked>\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Overlay Color\" name=\"overlayColor\" value=\"#ffffff\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Opacity\" name=\"overlayOpacity\" min=\"0\" max=\"1\" step=\"0.1\" value=\"0.3\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n    </mbr-parameters>\n    <div class=\"mbr-fallback-image disabled\" mbr-if=\"bg.type == 'video'\"></div>\n    <div class=\"mbr-overlay\" mbr-if=\"overlay && bg.type!== 'color'\" mbr-style=\"{'opacity': overlayOpacity, 'background-color': overlayColor}\"></div>\n    <div mbr-class=\"{'container': !fullWidth, 'container-fluid': fullWidth}\">\n        <div class=\"row justify-content-center\" mbr-if=\"showTitle || showText\">\n            <div class=\"col-md-12 content-head mb-5\">\n                <h1 class=\"mbr-section-title mbr-fonts-style  mb-0\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-title\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-1\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\"><b>Z čoho sa skladá?</b></h1>\n                <p class=\"mbr-subtitle mbr-fonts-style mt-4 mb-0\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showText\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-subtitle\">\n                    Great for pro-coders for fast prototyping and small customers' projects.\n                </p>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"row justify-content-center  blockContent\">\n            <div class=\"col-12 col-lg\">\n                <div class=\"item-wrapper align-left\">\n                    <div class=\"mbr-text counter-container mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text\" data-multiline mbr-article>\n                        <ol>\n                            <li><b>Dron RoboMaster TT </b>s integrovanou kamerou, stabilným riadením letu a presným polohovacím systémom.&nbsp;</li><li><b>Programovateľná riadiaca jednotka: </b>Umožňuje ovládanie robota v jazykoch Scratch, Python alebo Swift.</li><li><b>Inteligentné senzory: </b>Medzi iným výškomer, akcelerometer, gyroskop a snímače polohy pre presný pohyb.</li><li><b>Batéria a nabíjačka: </b>Rýchlo vymeniteľná batéria, ktorá je ideálna pre nepretržité používanie počas hodín.</li><li><b>Chránená konštrukcia: </b>Odolný kryt a ochrana vrtule pre bezpečné použitie v interiéri.</li></ol>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"col-12 col-lg-{{imageWidth}}\">\n                <div class=\"image-wrapper mb-4\">\n                    <img class=\"w-100\" src=\"@PROJECT_PATH@/assets/images/robomaster-tello-tt-talent-550.jpg\" alt=\"Mobirise Website Builder\">\n                </div>\n            </div>\n\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</section>",
