          "_name": "features05",
          "_sourceTheme": "startm5",
          "_customHTML": "<section data-bs-version=\"5.1\" class=\"features5\" group=\"Features\" data-bg-video=\"{{bg.type == 'video' && bg.value.url}}\" mbr-class=\"{'mbr-parallax-background': bg.parallax}\">\n  <mbr-parameters>\n    <header>Size</header>\n    <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Full Width\" name=\"fullWidth\">\n    <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Top\" name=\"paddingTop\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"6\">\n    <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Bottom\" name=\"paddingBottom\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"6\">\n    <header>Show/Hide</header>\n    <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Title\" name=\"showMainTitle\">\n    <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Subtitle\" name=\"showMainSubtitle\" checked>\n    <header>Card</header>\n    <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Title\" name=\"showTitle\">\n    <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Text\" name=\"showText\" checked>\n    <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Icons\" name=\"showIcon\" checked>\n\t<input type=\"checkbox\" name=\"showButtons\" title=\"Buttons\">\n    <input type=\"color\" title=\"Icon Color\" name=\"iconColor\" value=\"#edefeb\" selected condition=\"showIcon\">\n    <input type=\"color\" title=\"Icon BG\" name=\"iconbg\" value=\"#ffa600\" selected condition=\"showIcon\">\n    <select title=\"Columns\" name=\"columns\">\n      <option value=\"12\">1</option>\n      <option value=\"6\">2</option>\n      <option value=\"4\" selected>3</option>\n      <option value=\"3\">4</option>\n    </select>\n    <input type=\"color\" title=\"BG\" name=\"cardbg\" value=\"#ffffff\" selected>\n    <header>Background</header>\n    <fieldset type=\"background\" name=\"bg\" parallax>\n      <input type=\"image\" title=\"Image\" value=\"@PROJECT_PATH@/assets/images/background1.jpg\" parallax>\n      <input type=\"color\" title=\"Color\" value=\"#f7f7f7\" selected>\n      <input type=\"video\" title=\"Video\" value=\"https://vimeo.com/428046504\">\n    </fieldset>\n    <header condition=\"bg.type === 'video'\">Fallback Image</header>\n    <input type=\"image\" title=\"Fallback Image\" value=\"@PROJECT_PATH@/assets/images/background1.jpg\" name=\"fallBackImage\" condition=\"bg.type === 'video'\">\n    <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Overlay\" name=\"overlay\" condition=\"bg.type !== 'color'\" checked>\n    <input type=\"color\" title=\"Overlay Color\" name=\"overlayColor\" value=\"#ffffff\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n    <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Opacity\" name=\"overlayOpacity\" min=\"0\" max=\"1\" step=\"0.1\" value=\"0.5\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n  </mbr-parameters>\n\n  <div class=\"mbr-fallback-image disabled\" mbr-if=\"bg.type == 'video'\"></div>\n  <div class=\"mbr-overlay\" mbr-if=\"overlay && bg.type!== 'color'\" mbr-style=\"{'opacity': overlayOpacity, 'background-color': overlayColor}\"></div>\n  <div mbr-class=\"{'container': !fullWidth, 'container-fluid': fullWidth}\">\n    <div class=\"row mb-5 justify-content-center\" mbr-if=\"showMainTitle || showMainSubtitle\">\n      <div class=\"col-12 content-head\">\n        <h3 class=\"mbr-section-title mbr-fonts-style align-center mb-0\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-2\" mbr-if=\"showMainTitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-title\">\n          <b>Our Features</b>\n        </h3>\n        <h2 class=\"mbr-section-subtitle mbr-fonts-style align-center mb-0 mt-4\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-2\" mbr-if=\"showMainSubtitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-subtitle\"><b><i>Učenie, programovanie a inovácie v jednom drone!</i></b></h2>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"row\">\n      \n      <div class=\"item features-without-image col-12 col-md-6 col-lg-{{columns}} item-mb active\">\n        <div class=\"item-wrapper\">\n          <div class=\"card-box align-left\">\n            <div class=\"iconfont-wrapper\" mbr-if=\"showIcon\">\n              <span mbr-icon class=\"mbr-iconfont mobi-mbri-android mobi-mbri\"></span>\n            </div>\n            <h5 class=\"card-title mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\" data-app-selector=\".card-title, .iconfont-wrapper\">\n              <b>Creation</b>\n            </h5>\n            <p class=\"card-text mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showText\" data-app-selector=\".card-text, .item .mbr-section-btn\"><b>Crazyflie</b> je vynikajúca platforma pre výučbu robotiky, univerzitný výskum a inovatívne <b>projekty v oblasti STEM</b>. Rôzne výzvy – napríklad vnútorná lokalizácia, autonómna navigácia, let v roji (swarm) alebo vyhýbanie sa prekážkam – robia z učenia zážitok prostredníctvom reálnych inžinierskych problémov.<br></p>\n\n            <div class=\"mbr-section-btn item-footer\" mbr-if=\"showButtons\" data-toolbar=\"-mbrBtnMove,-mbrBtnAdd\" mbr-buttons mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\">\n              <a href class=\"btn item-btn btn-primary\" data-app-placeholder=\"Type Text\">Learn More</a>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div><div class=\"item features-without-image col-12 col-md-6 col-lg-{{columns}} item-mb\">\n        <div class=\"item-wrapper\">\n          <div class=\"card-box align-left\">\n            <div class=\"iconfont-wrapper\" mbr-if=\"showIcon\">\n              <span mbr-icon class=\"mbr-iconfont mobi-mbri-growing-chart mobi-mbri\"></span>\n            </div>\n            <h5 class=\"card-title mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\" data-app-selector=\".card-title, .iconfont-wrapper\">\n              <b>Promotion</b>\n            </h5>\n            <p class=\"card-text mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showText\" data-app-selector=\".card-text, .item .mbr-section-btn\">•<b> Otvorený zdrojový kód a voľne programovateľný:</b> podporuje vývoj v jazykoch Python a C.<br>• <b>Presné vnútorné polohovanie:</b> pomocou systému Lighthouse alebo Loco Positioning je možné dosiahnuť polohovanie s presnosťou na centimetre bez použitia GPS.<br>• <b>Let v rojovom režime a spolupráca:</b> je možné ovládať viacero dronov Crazyflie súčasne.<br>• <b>Bezpečné vzdelávacie prostredie:</b> malé rozmery, nízka hmotnosť a konštrukcia optimalizovaná pre použitie v interiéri.<br></p>\n\n            <div class=\"mbr-section-btn item-footer\" mbr-if=\"showButtons\" data-toolbar=\"-mbrBtnMove,-mbrBtnAdd\" mbr-buttons mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\">\n              <a href class=\"btn item-btn btn-primary\" data-app-placeholder=\"Type Text\">Learn More</a>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div><div class=\"item features-without-image col-12 col-md-6 col-lg-{{columns}} item-mb\">\n        <div class=\"item-wrapper\">\n          <div class=\"card-box align-left\">\n            <div class=\"iconfont-wrapper\" mbr-if=\"showIcon\">\n              <span mbr-icon class=\"mbr-iconfont mobi-mbri-hearth mobi-mbri\"></span>\n            </div>\n            <h5 class=\"card-title mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\" data-app-selector=\".card-title, .iconfont-wrapper\">\n              <b>Branding</b>\n            </h5>\n            <p class=\"card-text mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showText\" data-app-selector=\".card-text, .item .mbr-section-btn\"><b>Crazyflie </b>je malý mikrodron s otvoreným zdrojovým kódom, ktorý sa používa hlavne na vzdelávacie, výskumné a vývojové účely. Napriek svojim malým rozmerom a nízkej hmotnosti lieta stabilne a je možné ho vybaviť rôznymi senzormi. <b>Hardvér aj softvér</b> sa dajú voľne upravovať, takže používatelia na ňom môžu vyvíjať vlastné riadiace riešenia a autonómne funkcie.</p>\n\n            <div class=\"mbr-section-btn item-footer\" mbr-if=\"showButtons\" data-toolbar=\"-mbrBtnMove,-mbrBtnAdd\" mbr-buttons mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\">\n              <a href class=\"btn item-btn btn-primary\" data-app-placeholder=\"Type Text\">Learn More</a>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      \n    </div>\n  </div>\n</section>",
